    <title>Syria contributor: Luna Safwan</title>
    <description>Luna Safwan is a Lebanese journalist based in Beirut, currently working as a News Assistant with the Daily Telegraph, and as an Editor for Raseef22. She has been covering Syria since 2012 with a special focus on refugees, women &amp;amp; humanitarian violations. She previously worked for NOW News, The New Arab and has a BA in Journalism.
</description>
